reviewText:
I got this VCD very quickly shipped and it has helped strengthen my weak diaphragm which occurred from taking prednisone.
The breathing exercises are very helpful but my asthma got worse when I did the recommended amounts so I only do 10 minutes twice a week of Kabakbati breathing.
Not much explaination.  I don't know if you know the language in indian , would it be better.  For me , the english version really does not tell me much.
